</div></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-aa67ea562 one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_column vb-item" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-aa67ea562 mcb-item-column-inner"><div class="column_attr mfn-inline-editor clearfix" style="">LM Funding America, Inc. (Nasdaq: LMFA), together with its subsidiaries, is a cryptocurrency mining business that commenced Bitcoin mining operations in September 2022. The Company also operates a technology-based specialty finance company that provides funding to nonprofit community associations (Associations) primarily located in the state of Florida, as well as in the states of Washington, Colorado, and Illinois, by funding a certain portion of the Associations' rights to delinquent accounts that are selected by the Associations arising from unpaid Association assessments.

