</div></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-8f1c2d2a6 one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_column vb-item" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-8f1c2d2a6 mcb-item-column-inner"><div class="column_attr mfn-inline-editor clearfix" style=""><p>B2i Digital, Inc. leverages the latest digital marketing technologies to tell a company's story to retail investors, institutional investors, and research analysts. B2i Digital creates robust profiles for companies on its platform, <a tabindex="0" href="https://b2idigital.com/?hsLang=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-stringify-link="http://b2idigital.com" data-sk="tooltip_parent">b2idigital.com</a>, and launches targeted digital marketing campaigns to bring the most relevant investors to each company. The digital marketing strategy is combined with virtual and in-person conferences to increase the level of engagement between investors and companies. The company was founded in 2021 by David Shapiro, previously the Chief Marketing Officer for Maxim Group LLC and its investor awareness platform, <a tabindex="0" href="http://m-vest.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-stringify-link="http://M-Vest.com" data-sk="tooltip_parent">M-Vest.com</a>.</p></div></div></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-790a2a463 one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_button vb-item" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-790a2a463 mcb-item-button-inner"><a class="button  button_size_2" href="https://b2idigital.com/"     target="_blank"    title=""><span class="button_label">VISIT WEBSITE</span></a>
</div></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></div></div><style class="mfn-popup-tmpl-local-styles">#mfn-popup-template-11726:before{background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0.45);}</style><div data-id="11728" id="mfn-popup-template-11728"  class="mfn-popup-tmpl mfn-popup-tmpl-center mfn-popup-tmpl-width-default mfn-popup-tmpl-display-on-click mfn-popup-animate-fade-in mfn-popup-close-on-overlay-click mfn-popup-close-button-right mfn-popup-tmpl-close-button-show-on-start mfn-popup-browser-scroll-enabled"  data-closebuttondelay="3000"><div class="mfn-popup-tmpl-content"><a href="#" class="exit-mfn-popup exit-mfn-popup-abs">&#10005;</a><div class="mfn-popup-tmpl-content-wrapper"><div class="mfn-builder-content mfn-popup-tmpl-builder"><section class="section mcb-section mfn-default-section mcb-section-7220e8712  no-margin-h no-margin-v"   style="" ><div class="mcb-background-overlay"></div><div class="section_wrapper mfn-wrapper-for-wraps mcb-section-inner mcb-section-inner-7220e8712"><div  class="wrap mcb-wrap mcb-wrap-70c21ebbc one tablet-one laptop-one mobile-one vb-item clearfix" data-desktop-col="one" data-laptop-col="laptop-one" data-tablet-col="tablet-one" data-mobile-col="mobile-one" style=""   ><div class="mcb-wrap-inner mcb-wrap-inner-70c21ebbc mfn-module-wrapper mfn-wrapper-for-wraps"  ><div class="mcb-wrap-background-overlay"></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-0603ba2bf one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_image vb-item" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-0603ba2bf mcb-item-image-inner"><div class="image_frame image_item no_link scale-with-grid element_classes alignnone no_border mfn-img-box" ><div class="image_wrapper"><img width="600" height="300" src="https://spartancapital.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/calabrese-1.jpg" class="scale-with-grid" alt="" style="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://spartancapital.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/calabrese-1.jpg 600w, https://spartancapital.com/wp