</div></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-92560f614 one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_column vb-item" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-92560f614 mcb-item-column-inner"><div class="column_attr mfn-inline-editor clearfix" style=""><p>AmpliTech designs, develops, and manufactures custom leading-edge RF components for the Commercial, SATCOM, Space, and Military markets. These designs cover frequencies from 50 kHz to 44 GHz. AmpliTech also has developed new products for the 5G/6G wireless ecosystem and infrastructure with unparalleled performance. In addition to this rapidly emerging market, AMPG has also developed solutions for Quantum Computing, with cutting edge technology. We continue to blaze trails in our commitment to enable and accelerate the arrival of true 5G/6G architecture and contribute to the U.S. being the leader and first to reach the coveted position of Quantum Supremacy.</p></div></div></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-d5cab0f70 one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_button vb-item" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-d5cab0f70 mcb-item-button-inner"><a class="button  button_size_2" href="https://www.amplitechgroup.com/investor-relations"     target="_blank"    title=""><span class="button_label">VISIT WEBSITE</span></a>
