<p>The MUSQ Global Music Industry ETF (NYSE: MUSQ) seeks to provide investment results that, before fees and expenses, correspond generally to the total return performance of MUSQ Global Music Industry Index (<a tabindex="0" href="https://eqmindexes.com/musq-global-music-industry-index-summary/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MUSQIX</a>). The index aims to provide focused exposure to the entire music ecosystem and track companies with a core business interest in the global music industry.</p>
