</div></div></div></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-8c1cc2a7c one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_column vb-item" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-8c1cc2a7c mcb-item-column-inner"><div class="column_attr mfn-inline-editor clearfix" style=""><p>As a PCAOB-registered firm and the 52nd largest accounting firm in the nation, Grassi delivers high-quality audits with precision and expertise for public companies and those preparing for an IPO. Our SEC &amp; Capital Markets team provides hands-on guidance through IPOs, follow-on offerings, and equity and debt financing transactions. We tailor post-audit recommendations to your industry, ensuring ongoing compliance and strategic growth.</p>
