</div></div></div></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-2f7f7a80d one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_column vb-item" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-2f7f7a80d mcb-item-column-inner"><div class="column_attr mfn-inline-editor clearfix" style=""><p>NOUVEAU MONDE GRAPHITE (NYSE-NMG and TSX-NOU) is striving to become a key contributor to the sustainable energy revolution. The Company is working towards developing a fully integrated North American source of carbon-neutral battery anode material in Québec, Canada for the growing lithium-ion and fuel cell markets. It is fully permitted, construction ready, and has signed long-term binding and bankable offtakes with both General Motors and Panasonic Energy. With enviable ESG standards, NMG aspires to become a strategic supplier to the world’s leading battery and automotive manufacturers, providing high performing and reliable advanced materials while promoting sustainability and supply chain traceability.</p></div></div></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-53125fd56 one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_button vb-item" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-53125fd56 mcb-item-button-inner"><a class="button  button_size_2" href="https://nmg.com/investors/"     target="_blank"    title=""><span class="button_label">VISIT WEBSITE</span></a>
