id element_classes alignnone no_border mfn-img-box" ><div class="image_wrapper"><img width="280" height="88" src="https://spartancapital.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/lipella-white.png" class="scale-with-grid" alt="" style="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://spartancapital.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/lipella-white.png 280w, https://spartancapital.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/lipella-white-150x47.png 150w" sizes="auto, (max-width:767px) 280px, 280px" /></div></div>
</div></div></div></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-824206567 one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_column vb-item" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-824206567 mcb-item-column-inner"><div class="column_attr mfn-inline-editor clearfix" style=""><p>Lipella Pharmaceuticals Inc. is a clinical-stage biotechnology company focused on developing new drugs by reformulating the active agents in existing generic drugs and optimizing these reformulations for new applications. Our proprietary liposomal formulations are optimized for the delivery of agents to mucosal tissue, such as the oral cavity and the bladder lumen. Our pharmaceutical assets include a phase 2 program in oral lichen planus, and a phase 2 program in hemorrhagic cystitis.</p></div></div></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-4cdf1485d one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_button vb-item" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-4cdf1485d mcb-item-button-inner"><a class="button  button_size_2" href="https://ir.lipella.com/"     target="_blank"    title=""><span class="button_label">VISIT WEBSITE</span></a>
