</div></div></div></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-5a3287e27 one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_column vb-item" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-5a3287e27 mcb-item-column-inner"><div class="column_attr mfn-inline-editor clearfix" style=""><p>MySize, Inc. (NASDAQ: MYSZ) is a global leader in AI-powered size recommendation and digital commerce platforms for the fashion industry. With solutions like MySizeID and Naiz Fit, and its expansion into circular fashion through Percentil, MySize helps retailers improve fit, reduce returns, and enhance the customer journey—online and offline.</p></div></div></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-373253d42 one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_button vb-item" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-373253d42 mcb-item-button-inner"><a class="button  button_size_2" href="https://mysizeid.com/investors/"     target="_blank"    title=""><span class="button_label">VISIT WEBSITE</span></a>
